Hazaresha Salazan is an [[amnizu]] [[devil]] in [[Daanvi]] who loves to negotiate complex contracts. He considers himself faithful to the [[Keeper]] and often serves as a Talon, negotiating deals on the Lord of the Hoard's behalf.